Class Claim

    public final class Claim
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Claim>
    Class that contains a set of implements Parcelable Expenses, and details of a trip.

    This is an immutable class.

    See Claim.Builder on how to obtain an instance.
